SOAP web service Demo
---------------------

Contract first approach - defining formats beforehand
XSD - XML Schema Definition
JAXB - For XML Binding to Java objects

Steps for creating a SOAP service:
--------------------------------

1. Create an XML Schema Definition XSD file defining request and response formats.
2. Generate Java classes corresponding to the XSD using JAXB maven plugin (do in eclipse, intellij wont support)
3. Create Endpoint class with methods to accept the request and send response
4. Create a messageDispatcherServlet in ServletRegistrationBean
